snippet.title: Park Studio - Community Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Park Studio has an amazing community of talented builders, take a look at what they've built since the release of the game!


Get Park Studio today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2832220/Park_Studio/

Learn more about the game and what's coming: https://www.creyegames.com

Join the Community: https://discord.gg/dbHc2mQWAz


Recorded entirely in-game, content shown does not contain any rendered footage.
Recorded in Park Studio Alpha 0.2 Preview 1, using builds made in Alpha 0.1.2.
Recorded with a controller, on Epic default settings.
Content shown may contain placeholder assets.
